{"tid":2455691,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"砸1000萬為宮脇咲良慶生　粉送「奢華鑽戒」套牢…霸喊：不要嫁！","createTime":"2021-03-21T10:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T11:18:59.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef5bac3a344b2141b774d8b0bda7ff3bcfb4e347","tid":2455691,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"南韓「限定女團」IZ*ONE本月宣布解散，令大批歌迷感到不捨，其中日籍成員「小櫻花」宮脇咲良外型清純甜美、唱跳實力佳，在各地皆擁有高人氣，未來動向備受關注。她在19日迎來23歲生日，大陸粉絲為了替偶像慶祝，集資送出近4億韓圜（約1094萬台幣）的豪華大禮，引起關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5517/5517820.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5517%2F5517820.jpg&h=d8378b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼宮脇咲良在各地擁有高人氣。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／official_izone）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5517/5517821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5517%2F5517821.jpg&h=149d8b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了迎接宮脇咲良23歲生日，她的大陸粉絲後援會規劃了一系列慶生活動，包含電視台和地鐵站廣告投放、無人機燈光秀、公益捐款等等，更砸重金送上數十樣精品物件，品項囊括包包、飾品配件、衣物，光是禮物粗估花費就近千萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5517/5517824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5517%2F5517824.jpg&h=5c7d85f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼大陸粉絲砸千萬為宮脇咲良慶生。（圖／翻攝自微博／櫻綻_宮脇咲良個站）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5517/5517822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5517%2F5517822.jpg&h=9a128c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而在粉絲送出的數件豪禮中，還有一枚1.06克拉的鑽戒，據悉單價至少75萬台幣起跳，出手十分闊綽，同時向宮脇咲良霸氣喊話：「以後送鑽戒沒有粉絲送妳的貴的男人不要嫁！」奢華的禮品陣容引起網友關注，也令不少媒體看傻了眼，驚訝形容「像名品館一樣」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5517/5517823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5517%2F5517823.jpg&h=56b88cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲鑽戒至少75萬台幣。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n韓媒日前傳出，宮脇咲良與防彈少年團所屬經紀公司Big Hit娛樂聯繫密切，有望加入Big Hit娛樂大家族，更指出，她屆時有很高的可能性以女團身份亮相，Big Hit娛樂則隨後回應「還沒做出正式決定」，究竟下一步會如何規畫，粉絲都非常期待。"},{"pid":"b4153200b12cb4bbcf157a2e9feca8e98b670ef6","tid":2455691,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"唔好返去日本哩D垃圾地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380d75a39734e5147502c22ac5dc161a4e8055d7","tid":2455691,"uid":117802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:22:52.000Z","msg":"以後送鑽戒沒有粉絲送妳的貴的男人不要嫁<br />\n<br />\n拜金到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f0ef1e6c02d831c2e30d3305d71adde3379542","tid":2455691,"uid":80679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4153200b12cb4bbcf157a2e9feca8e98b670ef6","tid":2455691,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"唔好返去日本哩D垃圾地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"人地日本人點解唔番得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7108fd0a0be1f88efb646eb11828574e2b999521","tid":2455691,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24f0ef1e6c02d831c2e30d3305d71adde3379542","tid":2455691,"uid":80679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4153200b12cb4bbcf157a2e9feca8e98b670ef6","tid":2455691,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"唔好返去日本哩D垃圾地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"人地日本人點解唔番得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:36:58.000Z